As well as Wentz played, he could've done nothing without the infusion of fresh players HUNGRY to make a NAME for themselves!!!

The Eagles will have plenty of decisions to make. With the emergence of Ward Jr. & Bishop, our entire offense is rejuvenated. Carson's finally learning how to get rid of the football. We now have a solid rushing game again!!!

Agular will be moved, I'm sure of it. We can get something for Agular, hopefully.

Because of the resurgence of our offense, the defense is ON FIRE!!! When Cox got up from the injury, you KNEW it was the Eagles day!!!

When Ertz came back you KNEW it was the Eagles day!!!!

Skip, STOP CRYING, it was the EAGLES who were expected to run away with the Division & return to the Super Bowl!!!

All that appeared to be true, when Deshawn Jackson had that MONSTER GAME vs Washington, so DON'T CRY TO ME ABOUT INJURIES!!!
